* BMAP phase-8 listing control: TTL emits a title; LIST OFF suppresses the
* listing (ADA/STA are still assembled -- the PC advances -- but not shown)
* until LIST ON; EJECT emits a form feed.
       TTL    MY PROGRAM TITLE
       OUNAME LCTEST
       LDA    0
       LIST   OFF
       ADA    1
       STA    2
       LIST   ON
       LDQ    3
       EJECT
       STQ    4
       END
